{"tid":1733690,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"失意全因大意","createTime":"2019-11-18T07:10:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T08:21:35.000Z","uid":226846,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3eae01651495909697571f0b260327bddf645714","tid":1733690,"uid":226846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T07:10:44.000Z","msg":"我相信一哥一早就知道事情發展，呢個係一個超級大既分化計劃。<br />\n琴晚發生既事情，可以佢一早就諗到個結果。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢死守＝大家出去＝狗力防＝士氣大減＝打埋理大＝瓦解。<br />\n<br />\n所以呢個時候大家更要認真諗方法，如果結果都係捉左班義士，大家既思路係要諗點樣進化，宜唔係俾班3，5毛穩到位入去打擊士氣。<br />\n<br />\n你估一哥唔知真係救到理大既話自己會GG? <br />\n要記住希特勒咁勁都係因為賭贏左 法國輕視左德國佔領萊茵河畔。<br />\n所以大家要保持清晰。<br />\n戰爭第一課係觀察戰況。<br />\n戰爭首要係冷靜。<br />\nI Love HK"},{"pid":"a2d957cfce9c381c96209860b75dff4ab2b24e1b","tid":1733690,"uid":226846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T07:11:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2962c1f1c809535f36889adfb379f6e02d981de8","tid":1733690,"uid":226846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T07:11:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"905325559c14fde0a8daf41d1f219bccf6989e71","tid":1733690,"uid":226846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T07:11:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b53d17d1bcce6752c985f953fb84ee3e4c11192a","tid":1733690,"uid":226846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T07:12:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"782d304185a0b47ccbc0d22214bcfd1443fff74a","tid":1733690,"uid":226846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T07:13:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ffa90ee1b163af998b798f524780c27350dc1464","tid":1733690,"uid":226846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T07:13:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ada1142293e91e883ca9833aceb42447f7bf7792","tid":1733690,"uid":226846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T07:14:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fb526c7b52d97c2e61b04df750900acb536d0e2c","tid":1733690,"uid":226846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0